# Raw source material — NOT part of the deliverable.
# The assets the site needs are already normalised and copied into site/.
# Anchored to the repo root (leading /) so these never collide with
# same-named paths inside site/ (e.g. site/audio/music/) — git matching is
# case-insensitive by default on macOS, so an unanchored "Music/" here
# previously also matched and silently excluded site/audio/music/.
